Title
Inscribed information states that the deported woman is the headmaster Carolina Anjou. A seemingly older inscription on the back of photography indicates; Mrs Carolina Anjou? The following text presupposes that the woman is; Portrait of Carolina Anjou, born Elgérus. Daughter of the Handling and Councillor in Norrköping Daniel Gustav Elgérus and his spouse Carolina Elisabeth Cnattingius. Married in 1856 to the prospective principal at the Swedish School Seminar Christopher Ludvig Anjou
